{"tid":492374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂,同學仔,你好呀,呢到係ielts評估中心打比你","createTime":"2017-12-07T12:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T05:39:30.000Z","uid":143902,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf269f590c45777a9034ac0c8a675875d2afbb4","tid":492374,"uid":143902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"唔知各位巴打有冇聽過一個咁嘅電話<br />\n話說細佬我發夢果陣就返過呢份仆街工,做<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">電話聯絡員</span></span>,做落發覺入面完全係騙徒集中營<br />\n<br />\n一方面洗9人腦叫入面啲同事覺得自己係幫緊人,報ielts可以救佢一命,講撚到ielts可以幫人重獲新生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面又話叫人上泥試堂,但係其實幫你試堂條友可能係返左一兩個月嘅found dip 仔,總之目的係用撚盡方法叫你比撚左300蚊先<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢份工話就話係電話聯絡員,叫人試堂,其實根本係sell course, 比份電話list 上面又咩人都有,<span style=\"color: navy;\">唔知係咪有人賣資料</span>,仲有如果你身邊有人報左班,佢會叫佢地俾低身邊有興趣報ielts嘅人嘅電話比佢地<br />\n<br />\n返左幾日feel到唔撚對路就quit左,勸大家唔好返,聽到電話就cut 左佢,<span style=\"color: navy;\">當然有心嘅巴絲可以撚下狗</span>"},{"pid":"59c08f3549aa5283fba6251816322a1aa2fea7b5","tid":492374,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"去外國讀書咪有用，本地升學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c6c85d47392f2e96caa50da319ac54cc18d7f6","tid":492374,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"我都收過呢個電話，但打比我果個女仔係咁撩我傾閑計，我無野做又同佢傾左十幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n當然最後無受騙啦。"},{"pid":"80715dda4d4d6c65cb0672610132197a6b52f90b","tid":492374,"uid":143902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都收過呢個電話，但打比我果個女仔係咁撩我傾閑計，我無野做又同佢傾左十幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n當然最後無受騙啦。</blockquote><br />\n佢入面入教話要同人 build friendships, 令你覺得佢係你朋友,再令你上泥報班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fed0f30990ab438afdb7d9e42307eb2f5779f0","tid":492374,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"屌之前dse on99走去填問卷 係咁傾電話 當然次次約完都唔撚會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e1fdd933104ed9cf5d6417beddae493fa1f310","tid":492374,"uid":143902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌之前dse on99走去填問卷 係咁傾電話 當然次次約完都唔撚會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該兩三個月後又打比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fc44d34dfbca92db406921568a36f659ee4886","tid":492374,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話畢左業返緊工就無理我"},{"pid":"8254e80c36146c41e9ce5faa5f4759fa84b9e500","tid":492374,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:32:22.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw泥你老..."},{"pid":"8beb7fdaa3499a720f16f97ec2369ce066459631","tid":492374,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"push"}]}